text: Parliamentary elections were held in the People's Republic of Albania on 28 May 1950.Dieter Nohlen & Philip Stöver (2010) Elections in Europe: A data handbook, p133 Candidates were nominated by the Democratic Front, which was an organization subservient to the ruling Albanian Party of Labour.
